        "timestamp": "2018-03-20 23:35:26.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n(3 comments)\n\nFrom the code guidelines, I believe the correct implementation of a new paragraph in the javadoc is a blank line, followed by <p> at the start of new paragraph. I have replaced the </p> to align with this\n\n\"7.1.2 Paragraphs\nOne blank line—that is, a line containing only the aligned leading asterisk (*)—appears between paragraphs, and before the group of block tags if present. Each paragraph but the first has <p> immediately before the first word, with no space after.\"",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
